@page "/about"
@layout MainLayout

<div class="about-page">
    <section class="about-section">
        <h1>About Paul K.A. & Anticity Records</h1>

        <div class="about-content">
            <div class="about-text">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>
                    Founded in 2020 during the pandemic, Paul K.A. & Anticity Records emerged as a professional music production and licensing company.
                    What started as a creative outlet during uncertain times quickly evolved into a comprehensive music catalog with over 250 songs
                    spanning multiple genres and styles.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Our mission is to provide high-quality, original music for film, television, commercials, and video game developers.
                    We understand the power of music in storytelling and aim to enhance your creative projects with our diverse catalog.
                </p>

                <h2>Meet the Artists</h2>

                <div class="artist-profile">
                    <h3>Paul K.A.</h3>
                    <p>
                        As the founder and main producer of Anticity Records, Paul K.A. specializes in electronic music production.
                        His unique sound blends atmospheric textures with driving rhythms, creating versatile tracks perfect for a wide range of media projects.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="artist-profile">
                    <h3>Saul Before</h3>
                    <p>
                        Saul Before brings a diverse range of styles to Anticity Records, from punk to southern rock to metal.
                        His raw energy and authentic approach to music production adds depth and character to our catalog,
                        offering clients a wide spectrum of musical options.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="about-image">
                <img src="images/studio.jpg" alt="Anticity Records Studio" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="services-section">
        <h2>Our Services</h2>

        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>Music Licensing</h3>
                <p>
                    Choose from our extensive catalog of over 250 tracks across multiple genres.
                    We offer three licensing tiers to suit projects of any scale.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>Custom Music Production</h3>
                <p>
                    Need something specific? Our team can create custom music tailored to your project's unique requirements.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>Custom Licensing Agreements</h3>
                <p>
                    We understand that some projects have special needs. Contact us to discuss custom licensing options.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
